### Create order (expect 201)
# Assumes menu items 1,2 / discount 1 / tax 1 exist
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "items": [
    { "menuItemId": 1, "quantity": 1 },
    { "menuItemId": 2, "quantity": 2 }
  ],
  "discountIds": [1],
  "taxIds": [1]
}

###

### Get all orders (expect 200)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders

###

### Get order by id (expect 200 — snapshot values)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/1

###

### Update order — Option C (expect 200)
# Add item 3 (new snapshot), keep item 1 (retain old snapshot), remove item 2
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "menuItemId": 1, "quantity": 3 },
    { "menuItemId": 3, "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "discountIds": [1],
  "taxIds": [1, 2]
}

###

### Update order — empty items (expect 400)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/orders/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [],
  "discountIds": [],
  "taxIds": []
}

###

### Delete order (expect 204)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/orders/1

###

### Get deleted order (expect 404)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/1
